featureType.name: AMP_boundaries_PARK_simplified
featureType.title: Australian Marine Park (2025) PARK boundaries - simplified 1000m for querying
featureType.abstract: This layer represents the Australian Marine Park boundaries (aggregated by PARK), with a simplification algorithm (preserve critical points) of 1,000m applied. This layer is intended to be used for subsetting Squidle+ queries and is not designed to be published.
